features: 【5 in 1 Travel Power Strip with USB C Ports】: This short extension cord turns one wall outlet into 2 Widely AC outlets (15A/125V/1875W), 2 USB C ports and 1 USB A port, can power up to 5 essential travel gadgets simultaneously on your desk or nightstand from a small power strip. Extra space between each AC outlet on the compact power strip provides room for larger plugs, outlets are distributed in different sides without blocking.

【Compact for Travel & 12 inches Wrapped Extension Cord】 At only 5.36 oz, 4.72*2.5*1.8 inch mini size. 1ft retractable power cord with storage bag, compact and lightweight design makes it fit into luggage and bag easily. The 3 additional USB ports help also get rid of your bulky adapters. Ideal to bring during business travel, holiday and vacations to keep all your travel essential devices charged. It is also the best gift for your family.

【Desktop Power Strip with USB Ports】 This USB charging station with 3 USB ports, total 3.1 A/15W output, each USB-A port provide 5V/2.4A max, and USB-C port can up to 5V/3A max. With smart charging technology, the 2 Type-C and 1 USB-A ports will identify your devices automatically and deliver the fastest and most suitable charging speed. Great for most of your electronic devices that accepts fast charging (NOTE:The Type-C port doesn't support Macbook, Macbook Air, Macbook Pro or any other laptops which needs 14~22V charging voltage).

【Cruise Ship Essentials】: This travel extension cord with usb ports is designed with no surge protection, friendly for Cruise Ship (For Disney, Carnival, Royal Caribbean, please check with cruise company). The cruise power strip bring extra outlet and chargers instead of SINGLE outlet in the cruise cabin room,suitable for traveler cruise ships, hotels and airports. Making it a Travel Cruise Accessories Must Haves.

【Reliable Safety Travel Accessories】: The usb power strip is FCC & ETL approved and made of fire-resistant pc shell, making it fireproof up to 1382 F. Built-in short-circuit, over-voltage and over-current protection can ensure the safety. You can purchase with confidence, with our 30-day return and 12-month replacement.
